This is Zhang Tianming.

57
00:03:53,090 --> 00:03:54,830
Senior inspector of
Kowloon West Crime Unit.

58
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:55,739
He's highly regarded.

59
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:56,830
He's in charge of many cases.

60
00:03:57,610 --> 00:03:58,510
Nice to meet you, Boss.

61
00:03:58,850 --> 00:04:00,500
I'm responsible for
some of the major cases.

62
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,650
I hope I can be of use to you.

63
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,000
Inspector Zhang,

64
00:04:06,210 --> 00:04:07,329
I think one of your friends

65
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:08,179
is outside.

66
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:10,390
Why don't you invite him here?

67
00:04:27,650 --> 00:04:28,440
What is it?

68
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,830
Your friend is inviting you inside.

69
00:04:37,970 --> 00:04:39,019
Who is this?

70
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:40,760
Inspector Zhang, why don't you introduce him?

71
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:48,470
Will Inspector Liu be in danger?

72
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:50,200
Give him some time.

73
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:51,950
I'm sure he can deal with it.

74
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:55,630
He's my superior.

75
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:57,920
I don't know why he tailed me.

76
00:04:59,060 --> 00:05:00,560
Let me explain myself.

77
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:04,360
After the previous auction,

78
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,400
