79
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,470
of all the evidence.

80
00:05:08,290 --> 00:05:09,470
We cracked your PC as well.

81
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:11,630
But for some reason,

82
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:13,710
the PC was showing garbled texts.

83
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:15,950
Miss Zhuang was released
without any charges.

84
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:19,830
After that, I started suspecting him.

85
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:22,200
That's why I tailed him.

86
00:05:23,970 --> 00:05:25,320
But I never expected this.

87
