that I could get to know

89
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:31,880
all these major figures
before my retirement.

90
00:05:32,090 --> 00:05:33,760
Do you know how excited I am?

91
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,510
When it comes to ranking,

92
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:40,030
I'm the Chief Inspector of Police.
He's nothing.

93
00:05:41,170 --> 00:05:43,200
When it comes to experience
and connections,

94
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:45,999
do you think you can one-up me?

95
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:50,630
How can he replace Chief Ye?

96
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:52,699
He's just a minor figure.

97
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:54,070
He can't achieve anything.

98
00:05:55,850 --> 00:05:57,510
Do you guys want to consider me instead?

99
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,800
So, you were advertising yourself, huh?

100
00:06:02,850 --> 00:06:03,769
So, sir,

101
00:06:03,770 --> 00:06:05,440
