119
00:07:10,550 --> 00:07:11,120
Roger that.

120
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:12,409
Please keep an eye out.

121
00:07:12,410 --> 00:07:13,059
Okay.

122
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:14,070
Mustang, let's go.

123
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,650
All these years,

124
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:18,409
