177
00:09:20,690 --> 00:09:21,649
Boss!

178
00:09:21,650 --> 00:09:23,440
Boss, open the door!

179
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:24,590
Why did you shut them out?

180
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:27,019
This is a sacred Feng Shui room.

181
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:29,859
