evidence of Sundess's crime.

195
00:11:14,690 --> 00:11:15,590
Great job.

196
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:34,870
Inspector Liu!

197
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:45,800
Jiajie,

198
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:46,600
where are you?

199
00:12:46,650 --> 00:12:47,750
Inspector Liu is in trouble.

200
00:13:39,410 --> 00:13:40,259
Doctor, how is he?

201
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:41,160
I'm sorry.

202
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:13,680
Jiajie!

203
00:15:14,050 --> 00:15:15,160
Even if you kill him now,

204
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,650
there's no way to revive Inspector Liu!

205
00:15:16,690 --> 00:15:18,400
Sundess isn't dead!

206
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,350
He was supposed to be imprisoned
for the rest of his life.

207
00:15:22,350 --> 00:15:24,450
You set fire to the building
and implicated my brothers!

208
00:15:24,450 --> 00:15:25,710
You killed him!

209
00:15:25,810 --> 00:15:27,049
Officer, take him outside!

210
00:15:27,050 --> 00:15:27,619
Get out!

211
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:28,320
Let's go!

212
00:15:35,450 --> 00:15:37,950
Does he intend to bind his wife and daughter
with these shackles?

213
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:40,619
Just do your work.

214
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:41,640
Don't spout nonsense.

215
00:15:44,530 --> 00:15:45,320
Mommy.

216
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,520
Where's Jiao?

217
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:24,990
He's inside Inspector Liu's office.

218
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:42,950
My mother saw the news.

219
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:44,999
She found out
that Inspector Liu was killed.

220
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,750
She wanted me to resign immediately.

221
00:16:47,170 --> 00:16:48,560
You're the sole son of the family.

222
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:49,950
I can understand her feelings.

223
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:52,700
Indeed.

224
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:54,600
There's nothing more important than family.

225
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:56,070
What do you plan to do, then?

226
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:57,650
Inspector Liu once said

227
00:16:58,500 --> 00:17:00,999
that the most important trait
of a member of the Crime Unit

228
00:17:00,999 --> 00:17:02,160
is determination.

229
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:03,110
We should never give up.

230
00:17:04,300 --> 00:17:05,680
Now, Inspector Liu has left the unit.

231
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:08,100
We're responsible for
keeping the unit intact.

232
00:17:08,100 --> 00:17:09,150
All the more I cannot leave!

233
00:17:37,930 --> 00:17:39,030
Sorry for the trouble.

234
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:40,840
What else can I do for you?

235
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,450
He wasn't willing to say a word

236
00:17:42,450 --> 00:17:43,999
upon learning
that Sundess is still alive.

237
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:46,470
Let me give it a try.

238
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:47,950
But Mommy...

239
00:17:48,210 --> 00:17:49,470
I'll be fine. Don't worry.

240
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:50,920
Let's go.

241
00:18:13,450 --> 00:18:14,640
Someone wishes to see you.

242
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:22,360
I'm sorry.

243
00:18:27,380 --> 00:18:28,649
I'm not here today

244
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:30,310
as a police consultant.

245
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:33,200
I'm here as your wife.

246
00:18:36,540 --> 00:18:37,800
We've been together for so long.

247
00:18:38,850 --> 00:18:40,100
It turns out that you were hiding

248
00:18:40,110 --> 00:18:41,310
so many things from me.

249
00:18:43,010 --> 00:18:44,449
I couldn't help you out

250
00:18:44,450 --> 00:18:45,680
even after such a major incident.

251
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:48,500
I think I'm partly responsible
for your downfall.

252
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:52,790
Dear,

253
00:18:55,170 --> 00:18:56,400
can you promise me this?

254
00:18:56,650 --> 00:18:57,790
From now on,

255
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,310
stop hiding any secrets from me.

256
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:01,030
Be honest with me, okay?

257
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:02,750
We can face the hardships together.

258
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:14,270
I wish to know

259
00:19:14,970 --> 00:19:16,990
if he was Mai Zhihong's tutor,

260
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,000
how they got to know each other,

261
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,500
and why they planned
the murder together.

262
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:28,400
Are you Mai Zhihong's tutor?

263
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,400
How did you two get to know each other?

264
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:32,500
And, why did you two
plan the murder together?

265
00:19:36,650 --> 00:19:39,230
Fate is truly a magical thing.

266
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:43,270
I got to know Mai Zhihong

267
00:19:43,650 --> 00:19:45,160
on the day he wanted to commit suicide.

268
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:03,640
(Back then, I was passing by a garden.)

269
00:20:04,210 --> 00:20:06,160
(I saw Mai Zhihong
writing his last will.)

270
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,000
(I told him)

271
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:10,710
(that if he had the courage
to commit suicide,)

272
00:20:11,690 --> 00:20:13,400
(he should do
something meaningful instead.)

273
00:20:19,380 --> 00:20:20,840
(I did more than just save his life.)

274
00:20:21,450 --> 00:20:23,950
(I also knew
he was constantly bullied at school.)

275
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:26,550
(It's because he had
cognitive impairment.)

276
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,510
(He couldn't catch up
to his classmates.)

277
00:20:29,300 --> 00:20:30,790
(He was living in despair.)

278
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:34,950
(Chi Tak Secondary School Math Exercise)
(That's why I provided him with free lessons.)

279
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:38,400
For this question,

280
00:20:38,730 --> 00:20:40,470
it's asking you about AC.

281
00:20:41,010 --> 00:20:44,750
It is known that ABN
